  "explanation": "<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Perhaps</span> znači možda ili možda, ukazujući na to da nešto nije sigurno znano, ali ima mogućnost. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Perhaps we should check the logs again.</span> – Ovo prikazuje ideju bez sigurnosti.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Had</span> + subjekat + glagol u obliku <span class=\"highlighted-text\">past participle</span> predstavlja alternativu konstrukciji <span class=\"highlighted-text\">If</span> + subjekat + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">had</span> + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">past participle</span> i koristi se u rečenicama <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Third Conditional</span> za govor o hipotetičkim situacijama u prošlosti. Naglašava okolnost koja se nije dogodila, ali je mogla promeniti ishod. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Had we fixed the bug earlier, the system wouldn't have crashed.</span> - Ovo znači isto kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">If we had fixed the bug earlier, the system wouldn't have crashed.</span></p>\n</section>",
